data.enText: a disease that causes fever and shivering (= shaking of the body) caused by the bite of some types of mosquito

data.chText: 传播疟疾的昆虫；疟疾病人 / 流行区域

tr: an infective disease caused by sporozoan parasites that are transmitted through the bite of an infected Anopheles mosquito
marked by paroxysms of chills and fever

value.def: Malaria is a serious disease carried by mosquitoes which causes periods of fever.
